---

### ⚠️ MINOR INCONSISTENCIES

| Element | Inconsistency | Affected Screens | Recommendation |
|---------|---------------|------------------|----------------|
| **Modal Structure** | Different layouts | 1, 4 | Standardize modal: header (bg-gray-50), body (p-6), footer (pt-4, border-top) |
| **Search Input** | Different icon positions | 1, 2 | Always use `absolute left-3` for search icon |
| **Loading Spinner** | Different sizes/positions | 1-8 | Create reusable `<LoadingSpinner />` component |
| **Card Padding** | p-4, p-6, p-8 | All | Standardize: p-6 for data cards, p-8 for containers |
| **Grid Gaps** | gap-3, gap-4, gap-6 | All | Standardize: gap-6 for section grids, gap-4 for form grids |
| **Button Padding** | px-4/6 py-2/2.5 | All | Standardize: Primary (px-6 py-2.5), Secondary (px-4 py-2) |

---

### 🔴 MAJOR INCONSISTENCIES

| Issue | Evidence | Fix Required |
|-------|----------|--------------|
| **Unused `loading` state** | MarksEntry (line 17), ResultProcessing (line 18) | Remove or implement loading UI |
| **Unused `useEffect` import** | TranscriptGenerator (line 1) | Remove import or use for auto-fetch |
| **Hardcoded dropdown options** | 5 screens (3, 4, 5, 6, 8) | Replace with dynamic API calls |
| **Non-functional buttons** | 7+ screens (Edit, Delete, Archive, Save All, Lock, Download, Share, Print) | Wire up all interactive elements |

