- [ ] Example: "Failed to load sessions. [Retry Button]"

#### A3. Add Success/Error Notifications (6 screens)
- [ ] Install toast library: `react-hot-toast` or `react-toastify`
- [ ] Add success notifications after Create/Update/Delete operations
- [ ] Add error notifications on API failures
- [ ] Position: Top-right, auto-dismiss 3-5 seconds

#### A4. Fix Loading States (2 screens)
- [ ] **MarksEntry:** Display skeleton table when loading
- [ ] **ResultProcessing:** Show skeleton table when loading initial data

