### 📋 RECOMMENDED PRIORITIZATION

**Priority 1 (BLOCKERS):** Empty states, Error states, Toast notifications  
**Priority 2 (CORE UX):** Wire up all interactive buttons, dynamic dropdowns, form validation  
**Priority 3 (POLISH):** Accessibility, skeleton loading, confirmation dialogs  
**Priority 4 (REFACTOR):** Extract reusable components, reduce code duplication  

**ESTIMATED WORK REMAINING:** 40-50 hours for full UI completion

---

### ✅ DEPLOYMENT READINESS

**Current Status:** **NOT PRODUCTION-READY**

**Blockers:**
1. No error handling (app will crash on API failures)
2. No user feedback (users won't know if actions succeed/fail)
3. Many buttons appear clickable but do nothing (poor UX)

**Can Deploy to Staging:** ✅ YES (with known limitations documented)  
**Can Deploy to Production:** ❌ NO (must fix Priorities 1-2 first)

---

