3. **Add error states to all 8 screens** (2-3 hours)
4. **Wire up critical buttons** (Edit, Delete, Save All, Lock Marks) (4-6 hours)
5. **Replace hardcoded dropdowns with API calls** (2-3 hours)

**Total Immediate Work:** ~15-20 hours to achieve **80% completion** and staging-readiness.

